  "body_html": "<!DOCTYPE html\n  SYSTEM \"about:legacy-compat\">\n<html lang=\"en-us\" dir=\"ltr\"><head><title>Enter Prices/Net Present Values for Special Valuation</title><meta charset=\"utf-8\"><link rel=\"stylesheet\" type=\"text/css\" media=\"screen,projection\" href=\"/resource/css/style-v2.css\"><script type=\"text/javascript\" src=\"js/sap-strings.js\"></script></head><body class=\"en-us sap-light centered navigation-default enumeration-disabled\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-container\" class=\"container_12\" role=\"application\"><div id=\"d4h5-section-container\" class=\"grid_12\"><div id=\"d4h5-main-content\" class=\"grid_8 alpha omega\"><section><div class=\"page topic  - topic-topic \" id=\"loiocc0ada531198434de10000000a174cb4\"><h1 class=\"title topictitle1\">Enter Prices/Net Present Values for Special Valuation </h1><div class=\"body\">\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Use\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"> Enter a special price (for securities) here which can differ from the current market price or the net present value (for loans).\n</p>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Integration\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Integration</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"> The values in this table are needed in order to carry out a special valuation or for recording impairments.\n</p>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Features\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Features</h2>\n<p class=\"p\"> The price / impairment price or net present value / impairment value is defined per position depending on the position differentiations.\n</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> Company code</span>\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> Valuation area</span>\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> Valuation class</span>\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Securities:\n</p><ul class=\"ul\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> ID number</span>\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> Securities account, securities account group</span> or <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">portfolio</span>\n</p></li></ul></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Loan\n</p><ul class=\"ul\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"><span class=\"ph uicontrol\"> Contract number</span>\n</p><aside class=\"note caution\" aria-labelledby=\"n0t\"><div class=\"title\" id=\"n0t\"><strong>Caution</strong></div>\n<p class=\"p\"> For single position management\n</p></aside></li></ul></li></ul>\n</section></div>\n<div class=\"section\"><section class=\"section\" type=\"Activities\"><h2 class=\"section_title\">Activities</h2>\n<ol class=\"ol\"><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Enter the <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">valuation key date</span> for which you want to specify the prices/net present values.\n</p></li><li class=\"li\"><p class=\"p\"> Choose <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Execute.</span>\n</p></li></ol>\n</section></div>\n</div></div></section><div class=\"clear\"></div>\n</div></div></div></body></html>"
